    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Cutthroat Trout</strong>: Found in wild streams and mountain creeks, often catch-and-release.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brook Trout</strong>: Thrive in high-elevation cold streams and shaded pools.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brown Trout</strong>: Rare but present in some rivers and deeper water stretches.
    </li>
</ul>
